From 4b716ee1760358dca60d2b8012df1a67fc977f92 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Christopher L. Crutchfield" <ccrutchf@ucsd.edu>
Date: Sun, 3 May 2026 00:42:05 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/7] phy: samsung-gs101-ufs: add missing END_UFS_PHY_CFG to
 pre_pwr_hs table
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

tensor_gs101_pre_pwr_hs_config[] was missing the terminator entry. The
samsung_ufs_phy_config -> for_each_phy_cfg walker iterates while
cfg->id != 0, so without END_UFS_PHY_CFG it reads off the array end
into the next-adjacent rodata, which is tensor_gs101_post_pwr_hs_config[].

At HS pre-PMC, this means the entire post_pwr_hs table currently fires
during pre_pwr_hs:

  [intended] PHY_TRSV_REG_CFG_GS101(0x369, 0x11, PWR_MODE_ANY)
  [intended] PHY_TRSV_REG_CFG_GS101(0x246, 0x03, PWR_MODE_ANY)
  [unintended] PHY_COMN_REG_CFG(0x8, 0x60, PWR_MODE_PWM_ANY)
  [unintended] PHY_TRSV_REG_CFG_GS101(0x222, 0x08, PWR_MODE_PWM_ANY)
  [unintended] PHY_TRSV_REG_CFG_GS101(0x246, 0x01, PWR_MODE_ANY)
  [legitimate sentinel from post_pwr_hs] END_UFS_PHY_CFG

Note in particular that entry 5 writes 0x246=0x01, overwriting entry 2's
0x246=0x03 written one entry earlier. samsung_ufs_phy_config does not
filter on cfg->desc — the PWR_MODE_PWM_ANY tags are advisory only —
so the PWM-only writes fire on every HS pre-PMC.

Discovered by diffing AOSP gs201 cal-if pre_pmc against this driver +
ufs-exynos.c gs101_ufs_pre_pwr_change. Top candidate for the
gs201 HS dl_err 0x80000002 wedge that mainline hits on the first frame
after PMC. Fix verification pending on Pixel Fold (gs201).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 drivers/phy/samsung/phy-gs101-ufs.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/phy/samsung/phy-gs101-ufs.c b/drivers/phy/samsung/phy-gs101-ufs.c
index af1938034c29..6f014279200c 100644
--- a/drivers/phy/samsung/phy-gs101-ufs.c
+++ b/drivers/phy/samsung/phy-gs101-ufs.c
@@ -111,6 +111,7 @@ static const struct samsung_ufs_phy_cfg tensor_gs101_pre_init_cfg[] = {
 static const struct samsung_ufs_phy_cfg tensor_gs101_pre_pwr_hs_config[] = {
 	PHY_TRSV_REG_CFG_GS101(0x369, 0x11, PWR_MODE_ANY),
 	PHY_TRSV_REG_CFG_GS101(0x246, 0x03, PWR_MODE_ANY),
+	END_UFS_PHY_CFG,
 };
 
 /* Calibration for HS mode series A/B */
